and is equivalent to <em>any other non-terminating program</em>, e.g. <code class="highlighter-rouge">WHILE BTrue DO SKIP END</code>: (å› ä¸ºæˆ‘ä»¬çš„ã€Œç­‰ä»·ã€åªè¦æ±‚åŒã€Œå‘æ•£ã€å³å¯)</p>

