</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<blockquote>
  <p>åœ¨ commands ä¸Šç­‰ä»·ä½†ä¸åŒä½™çš„å…³ç³»?</p>
</blockquote>

<p>I guessâ€¦â€œboth terminatingâ€ relation?
which is equivalence relation on commands, but the equivalence would not be maintained after, say <code class="highlighter-rouge">C_WHILE</code> operation.</p>

